text: Willisau is a town of the district of Willisau in the canton of Lucerne in Switzerland. ==History== On 1 January 2006, the former municipalities of Willisau Land (W. Country) and Willisau Stadt (W. Town) merged into the new town of Willisau. On 1 January 2021, Gettnau became a part of Willisau. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website of the town of Willisau * Category:2006 establishments in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Willisau Category:Cities in Switzerland
